Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:21.94,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}You changed me so much I don't remember what I was like before we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:26.43,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The breeze caresses our cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:28.54,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Lullaby of Birdland...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:32.76,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}As we run down the slope,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:36.82,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}our flimsy shadows extend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:41.76,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's like a neverending summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:47.27,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It feels like when we snuck into the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:53.30,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Yeah, let's swim with our clothes on. Jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:55.99,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's an intense spiral of temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:01:00.51,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}A beat pierces my heart. A strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.00,0:01:04.08,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It vanishes after a quick spark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:06.88,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Even on bad days, I dress up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:11.87,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}and dance to some swing. The music quickly surrounds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:14.72,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}What is this dance exactly? I can't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:23.98,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Don't leave me. It's stuck in my head, and I can't get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:27.07,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The melody...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:32.86,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}is like love.
