Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:10.87,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:13.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't let myself get my hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:15.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I've already been rejected once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:25.47,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have the usual, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:26.79,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, the usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:28.67,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:30.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking beautiful as always, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:33.55,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:36.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:37.85,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:41.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in shock over the news that Yurika eloped?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.84,0:02:45.31,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.98,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you tell him about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.77,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kawabuchi? I told him this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:54.69,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he's in the classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:58.03,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect to hear anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:00.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,How must he feel about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:19.21,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's the one that won the \NPrefectural Governor's Award.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:21.54,Main Dialog,Boy B,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better take it down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:23.08,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,You take that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:25.06,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:28.01,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way the school will display
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:30.08,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,a painting by a student who's involved in a scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.95,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,We were told to remove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:34.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,And what's going to happen to it after you take it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:35.56,Main Dialog,Boy B,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This painting is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:40.67,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:44.37,Main Dialog,Boy B,0000,0000,0000,,What's she to you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:47.12,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,Had eyes for her, did ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.06,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:49.67,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:55.33,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. You can take it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:57.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:01.58,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sen! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:03.72,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you care what happens to that painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:04.14,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.89,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:11.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you laughing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:13.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Your stupidity must be contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:15.83,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:20.68,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, how stupid are you gonna be for somebody else's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:21.57,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:24.70,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, so what about the painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:27.94,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I already said my goodbye to it back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:30.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I feel much better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:39.80,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:43.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotten a present \Nfrom someone recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Like something that was knitted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.72,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:53.48,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I knitted Sentaro a sweater and used \Nthe leftover yarn to make the mittens!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:57.02,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's cruel, but it figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:59.77,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This. It's called Lily-yarn or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:02.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sachiko gave it to me yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:03.56,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:05.49,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:09.99,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But what am I supposed \Nto do with this string?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:17.50,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:20.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing? You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:26.51,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're gonna get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:27.89,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:30.26,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:39.72,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, these are really warm. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:43.57,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Damn it! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:46.07,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.87,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.75,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, we'll be \Nchanging classes again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:01.25,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I guess third-years are split up \Naccording to their grades,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:04.28,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,so you probably won't be in \Nthe same class as Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.68,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Goin' for college entrance exams, right, Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.76,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:13.13,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm planning on going to college too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:16.84,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking about becoming \Nan elementary school teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:19.47,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,So you're gonna be a teacher, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:20.56,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:25.58,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, you said you wanted \Nto have a bakery or cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:28.10,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What? When was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:31.03,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't you remember? \NYou were a glutton.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.53,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you wanted an entire shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:35.37,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:38.91,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, where do you want to go to college?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:44.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I... haven't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:47.92,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,As for me, never mind about college.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:50.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I might not even make it to third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:51.94,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:55.43,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.10,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,All right, everything depends on the next make-up exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:02.26,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Start with these basic problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:04.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you some flash cards in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:06.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:09.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:12.07,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just not cut out for studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:14.53,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do if you fail this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:17.34,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll just quit school an' get a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:19.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You must be jo—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:20.52,apollon 2nd,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:24.39,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about my family,\NI can't afford to repeat a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:27.05,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:29.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:31.63,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let you flunk this test!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:55.95,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired. I need a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:57.86,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! You're in the middle of these questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:08:00.08,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:03.02,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to rest, it'll have to wait till you're done with these problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.83,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! My head's gonna explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.41,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.14,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:24.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You look really happy when you're surrounded by the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.55,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where'd that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:29.98,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're going to have \Na big family of your own,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:32.80,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,and have lots of kids around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.83,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:41.36,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Chi'ko wet herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:41.36,apollon 2nd,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wet herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:43.19,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, Chi'ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,The bath's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:53.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My ma will dry your pants,\Nso relax till they're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:09:00.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This is an unusual setup for a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:03.10,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:07.62,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're out of soap, right? Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:18.62,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:23.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this Sen's family's bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:27.62,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Our families share it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:36.94,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I wish I had given you those mittens earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:42.04,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost spring, so you won't \Nneed to use them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:51.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Since you knitted them, I'd like to wear them all year round.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:53.77,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:56.03,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Condensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:59.24,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Drops often fall in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:02.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro lets out a yelp once in a while himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:08.76,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,So, why did you give me those mittens?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:12.16,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:15.80,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why me and not him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:25.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if you've liked him all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:38.90,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie! How about havin' dinner here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:41.62,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Your pants aren't dry yet anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:43.37,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:45.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:49.75,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, your hair's soakin' wet!\NYou'll catch cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:50.83,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:55.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:58.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:07.74,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to say that to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:12.10,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't get the idea out of my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:17.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,that she probably still has feelings for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.71,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sen, how did the make-up exam go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.76,0:11:34.09,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:34.59,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:36.20,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:37.95,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:38.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta thank 'im proper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:42.58,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I haven't\Nseen him around lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:45.22,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,The day before yesterday, he \Npassed out in class with a fever,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.14,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,so he's restin' up at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.30,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:51.33,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, Ritsuko didn't say a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:18.05,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,"Someday My Prince Will Come"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:22.38,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! That was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:25.55,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko, would you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:33.78,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Look, isn't his house huge?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.42,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,All right, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:39.60,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Thank him for me for helpin' me study.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:40.31,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:41.32,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:43.21,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Go on by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:46.82,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Let's go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:53.25,Main Dialog,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, one of your classmates \Nhas come to wish you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.21,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:59.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:05.25,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is your fever down?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:08.43,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sorry to make you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:10.84,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:14.27,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. These are for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.81,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Eat them if you're up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:20.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you go out of your way to buy them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:26.32,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um, no. I didn't buy these. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.78,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:34.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri, he came here with you, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.83,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you two out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:39.37,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He should've come in with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:41.21,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:45.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:47.40,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:49.43,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:52.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You two have been together since you were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:55.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could be a match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:14:01.36,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike me, he's strong and built.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:05.36,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He's so handsome that he even takes my breath away once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:09.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're better off with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:10.70,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:17.83,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you're saying, \Nso don't say any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:21.34,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:32.11,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, don't you like me anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.11,0:14:33.35,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:37.88,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,you just don't have any confidence, \Nso you're trying to keep your distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:43.61,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You told me to have confidence in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:48.11,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Those words have saved me a number of times now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:52.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But if it looks like you don't have confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:54.95,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling I'll lose mine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:04.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What the heck am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:09.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What I've wished for all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:12.96,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:15.01,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:19.98,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:23.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet something happened between those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:28.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:31.53,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:35.03,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come here! I'll go over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:55.30,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri, let me tell you how I feel\Nabout you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:58.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:02.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Ri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.46,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I love you! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:05.58,apollon 2nd,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:05.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:10.03,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please! Your relatives can hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Let them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:21.46,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not muscular, and maybe I'm \Nnot as manly as I should be,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:26.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but when it comes to my feelings for you, I'm second to no one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:33.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You might catch my cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:35.96,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I won't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:41.85,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:45.86,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're burning up! And you're heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:48.77,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:51.04,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,That was really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:51.68,apollon 2nd,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru! Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:05.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's already summer, and I haven't made any more progress with Ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:08.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I was so bold when I had that fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:10.92,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with me when \Nmy temperature is normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:13.67,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:15.16,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Touch what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:16.86,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:17.52,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:18.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.00,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:20.19,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:22.64,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you! Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.77,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,"The Olympus Has Thrown Down the Gauntlet"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:27.24,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:32.02,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,"The Olympus is going to win at this year's festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:35.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru to Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,It seems there are still some \Nold-fashioned jazz musicians around,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:38.41,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,but this is the era of rock n' roll."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:41.41,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,They were handing this \Nout all over the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.32,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:45.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't take this sitting down, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:47.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You two are gonna perform in the festival, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:50.52,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:53.92,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:54.94,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:59.82,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,We start with "Moanin'" to fire up \Nthe people that saw us last year
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:02.68,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,an' trick 'em into thinking we're \Ngonna do the same routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:05.98,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,But then we move into some other \Nsongs that we want to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.56,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinkin' the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:11.12,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's choose our next song!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:13.65,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, we'd better \Npractice every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.65,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,'Course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:16.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:20.70,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:23.13,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:23.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:24.10,apollon 2nd,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:25.54,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I got surprising news!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:28.38,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Dad says he's comin' home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:30.72,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,This way, the whole family can live together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:39.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:43.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:53.46,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that I'm actually scared, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:54.44,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:19:01.41,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,See, our Dad, who was working far \Naway, is coming home tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:06.58,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, I'm one of those that ain't got a place in the house too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:12.20,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:15.95,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:18.42,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're back late, Sachiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:22.77,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's Richie doin' here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:29.45,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Unlike Kota and the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:32.83,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,you remember how scary Dad \Nwas when he was drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:35.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry, Sachiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:40.96,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ma told me that he worked really \Nhard an' quit drinkin' over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:43.07,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:46.33,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You got nothin' \Nto worry about, Sachiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.95,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Now how about comin' inside \Nan' we can prepare together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:50.51,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:53.83,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:59.34,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks for lookin' after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:03.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one I'm worried about, Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:14.33,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Dope! What are you lookin' so serious for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:17.65,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What? I am serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:20.65,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, don't worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.84,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:26.28,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:27.25,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Comin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:27.53,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:31.29,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you coming to practice tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:38.34,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. After all, playin' with \Nyou is the most fun I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:49.56,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, what are you writin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:52.56,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... Nah, that's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:54.56,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's not comin' out right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:59.43,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well. Let's get to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:10.43,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, I'm sorry for lying to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:15.37,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking forward to the\Nfestival too. I wanted to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:18.45,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Be good to Ri'ko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:20.84,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
